Mauritius Development Trust Rises to 16-Year High on Dividend

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-06-29T07:54:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-29/mauritius-development-trust-rises-to-16-year-high-on-dividend.html
Mauritius Development Investment
Trust Co. rose to its highest intraday level since 1995 after
announcing a final dividend for the year through June.  The stock rallied 0.1 rupee, or 1.8 percent, to 5.8 rupees
at 11:35 a.m., in  Port Louis , the capital.  MDIT, as the company is known, said after market closure
yesterday that it will pay a final dividend of 0.21 rupee for
the year ending June 30.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  